<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/alpento.1.20669.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Drosophila guayllabambae Rafael & Arcos, 1988 (Drosophila repleta group, Drosophila hydei subgroup). 1 km NE of Estacion Ferrocarril de Machu Picchu, Cuzco, Peru, 02. III. 1984, C. R. Vilela coll., male terminalia (MZSP). A, epandrium, cerci and surstyli, oblique posterior view. B, surstyli and decasternum, posterior view. C, hypandrium and gonopods, posterior view. D-H, aedeagus, paraphyses and aedeagal apodeme, several views from dorsal through ventral. Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/168899" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

